Write a program to count the number of digits in a given integer.

Input Format

A single integer N

Constraints

0 ≤ N ≤ 10⁹

Output Format

Print the number of digits.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
#include <math.h>
#include <stdlib.h>

int main() {

    int n,count;
    scanf("%d",&n);
    while(n>0){
        count++;
        n/=10;
               
    }  
    printf("%d",count)  ;
    return 0;
}
